      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"break\" doesn't feel like it would be enough. It's like this constant, crushing weight in my chest that won't go away. I just want the silence to stop being so loud. I just want everything to just... stop. Is that even a normal way to feel? To just want it all to end?",
