    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say it won't last forever, but what if it does? what if this is just how it is now? it feels like i'm just dragging myself through the days for no reason at all. it's so exhausting to keep trying when there's nothing left to care about. it feels more like a burden than a life lately.",
